When you attune with this ring you sense a deeper perception of your surroundings.

While worn and attuned this plain dull band increases your [skill]Perception[/skill] (and [rules]Passive Perception[/rules]) by +3. It often constricts slightly and sometimes glows dimly blue when there may be something worth noticing. Companions and creatures within 5' may notice your ring glowing.

You may cast [spells]Detect Magic[/spells] with a [action]Magic[/action] action 1/day using this ring. Spells cast with this ring require no [rules]concentration[/rules].

When another magic item grants a greater bonus to Perception or Passive Perception this ring may still be used to cast spells.

Crafting this ring requires a bit of [monster]Weasel[/monster].
